#

Lobster Thermidor

$75
900 kcal
Difficulty: 80%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

shellfishdairyeggs

Dietary Tags:

high-proteinlow-carb

Tags:

gourmetseafoodFrench cuisine

Description

A luxurious lobster dish with a creamy, cheesy filling and a crispy Parmesan crust, finished with garlic herb butter.

Ingredients

  • lobster tails: 4 large
  • butter: 1/2 cup
  • shallots: 2, finely chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • cognac: 1/4 cup
  • white wine: 1/2 cup
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • Dijon mustard: 1 tablespoon
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • egg yolks: 2
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • parsley: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • thyme: 1 teaspoon, fresh
  • bread crumbs: 1/2 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
